00:11:51,627 --> 00:11:53,838
(laughing)

288
00:11:53,921 --> 00:11:55,297
BARNEY:
That's a new one!

289
00:11:55,381 --> 00:11:57,174
Wait a minute.

290
00:11:57,258 --> 00:11:58,968
(laughing)

291
