298
00:12:12,189 --> 00:12:14,191
(yelps)

299
00:12:14,275 --> 00:12:15,818
Come on, come on.
Make it, make it, make it.

300
00:12:15,901 --> 00:12:17,820
Please, please, please.

301
00:12:17,903 --> 00:12:19,488
I want to watch Krusty.

302
00:12:19,572 --> 00:12:20,531
Shut up, boy.

303
00:12:20,614 --> 00:12:21,574
