this field goal,

304
00:12:21,657 --> 00:12:22,658
I win 50 bucks.

305
00:12:25,786 --> 00:12:26,912
ANNOUNCER:
<i>The kick is up.</i>

306
00:12:26,996 --> 00:12:28,664
<i>It's looking good.</i>

307
00:12:28,748 --> 00:12:31,959
<i>The ball is turning into</i>
