308
00:12:32,042 --> 00:12:33,794
<i>Aahh!... oof!</i>

309
00:12:33,878 --> 00:12:36,714
ANNOUNCER: <i>And it's no good,</i>
<i>and you know what we say</i>

310
00:12:36,797 --> 00:12:38,507
<i>every time</i>
<i>something strange happens--</i>

311
00:12:38,591 --> 00:12:40,760
<i>it's good that</i>
<i>Bart did that.</i>

312
00:12:40,843 --> 00:12:42,136
<i>It's very good.</i>

313
00:12:42,219 --> 00:12:44,513
<i>(weary laugh)</i>

314
00:12:44,597 --> 00:12:46,766
<i>Well, we're still on.</i>

315
00:12:46,849 --> 00:12:48,559
<i>346 consecutive hours</i>

316
00:12:48,642 --> 00:12:52,563
